├── DialogBackdrop   (z-index: context.allocate_claim() → 1000)   ← sibling, not parent
├── DialogContent    (z-index: context.allocate_claim() → 1001)
├── NestedBackdrop   (z-index: context.allocate_claim() → 1002)
